      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Low"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is straightforward, involving a simple selection of a user ID followed by an update operation. It does not involve complex logic, loops, or error handling, making it relatively easy to understand and maintain."
        }
      ]
    },
